     H            Y.
     F** AL#RG0 **************************************
     F* UPDATE CUSTOMER PER TRUCK M/F                *
     F*        KIRI         2016.08.12               *
     F************************************************
     FAL#PWG0 CF  E                    WORKSTN
      *
     FAL#PPG1 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *
     FFGBPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     FAL#PLC1 IF  E           K        DISK
      *================================================================
     E                    ER      1  20 65
      *
     E                    @UK        40  2
     E                    D2UK       40  2
      *================================================================
     I            DS
     I                                        1   2 D2NUK1
     I                                        3   4 D2NUK2
     I                                        5   6 D2NUK3
     I                                        7   8 D2NUK4
     I                                        9  10 D2NUK5
     I                                       11  12 D2NUK6
     I                                       13  14 D2NUK7
     I                                       15  16 D2NUK8
     I                                       17  18 D2NUK9
     I                                       19  20 D2NUKA
     I                                       21  22 D3NUK1
     I                                       23  24 D3NUK2
     I                                       25  26 D3NUK3
     I                                       27  28 D3NUK4
     I                                       29  30 D3NUK5
     I                                       31  32 D3NUK6
     I                                       33  34 D3NUK7
     I                                       35  36 D3NUK8
     I                                       37  38 D3NUK9
     I                                       39  40 D3NUKA
     I                                       41  42 D4NUK1
     I                                       43  44 D4NUK2
     I                                       45  46 D4NUK3
     I                                       47  48 D4NUK4
     I                                       49  50 D4NUK5
     I                                       51  52 D4NUK6
     I                                       53  54 D4NUK7
     I                                       55  56 D4NUK8
     I                                       57  58 D4NUK9
     I                                       59  60 D4NUKA
     I                                       61  62 D5NUK1
     I                                       63  64 D5NUK2
     I                                       65  66 D5NUK3
     I                                       67  68 D5NUK4
     I                                       69  70 D5NUK5
     I                                       71  72 D5NUK6
     I                                       73  74 D5NUK7
     I                                       75  76 D5NUK8
     I                                       77  78 D5NUK9
     I                                       79  80 D5NUKA
     I                                        1  80 D2UK
     I                                        1  80 D2UKX
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140@TIME
     I                                        1   60@SYSTM
     I                                        7  140@SYSHZ
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *================================================================
      * CONTROL                                            *
      *================================================================
     C                     MOVE '#INIT   '@STEP   8
     C*
     C           @STEP     DOUEQ'#END    '
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#INIT   '#INIT
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP1   '#DSP1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK1   '#CHK1
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#DSP2   '#DSP2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2   '#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#CHK2 F5'#CHK2
     C           @STEP     CASEQ'#UPD    '#UPD
     C                     ENDCS
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   K  E  Y   L  I  S  T                             *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1SURT
     C                     KFLD           D1DATE
     C           KEY03     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     KFLD           D1DATE           CHANGE DATE
     C                     KFLD           D1TOKU           COSTOMER CODE
     C                     KFLD           D1NONY           DELIVERY CODE
     C                     KFLD           D1NKOJ           DELIVERY FACTORY
     C                     KFLD           K1NUKE  4        DOCK
      *================================================================
      * INIT                                               *
      *================================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVEA*ALL'0'   *IN
     C                     TIME           @TIME
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADD3411      D1TOKU           COSTOMER CODE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1NONY           DELIVERY CODE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1NKOJ  1        DELIVERY FACTORY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
      *
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      * DSP 1
      *================================================================
     C           #DSP1     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     EXFMTDSP01
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,11
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     SETOF                     111213
     C                     SETOF                     1415
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
      *--------------------
     C                     SELEC
     C** < F1 >
     C           *INKA     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#END    '@STEP
     C** < F7 >
     C           *INKG     WHEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'AL#CG1'
     C** < F8 >
     C           *INKH     WHEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'AL#RG8'
     C** < F12 >
     C           *INKL     WHEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'AL#RG1'
     C                     PARM           P1DATE  80       CHANGE DATE
     C           P1DATE    IFNE *ZERO
     C                     Z-ADDP1DATE    D1DATE
      *
     C                     CALL 'AL#RC8'
     C                     PARM           P1DATE           CHANGE DATE
     C                     PARM           P1SURT  9        SUB ROUTE
     C           P1SURT    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVE P1SURT    D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C**
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C**
     C                     OTHER
     C                     MOVE '#CHK1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDSL
      *--------------------
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *          DSP1 CHECK
      *================================================================
     C           #CHK1     BEGSR
      * UPDATE(11)
     C                     SELEC
     C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '0'
     C                     MOVE 'CANCEL'  D2KKBN
     C                     SETON                     18    <PR>
     C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE 'CHANGE'  D2KKBN
     C                     SETOF                     1819  <CS>
     C           D1KKBN    WHEQ '2'
     C                     MOVE 'ADD   '  D2KKBN
     C                     SETOF                     1819  <CS>
     C                     OTHER
     C                     SETON                     11  99
     C                     MOVELER,1      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDSL
      * DATE
     C           D1DATE    IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     15  99
     C                     MOVELER,15     D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE D1DATE    P$DATE
     C                     CALL 'DATR10'
     C                     PARM           P$DATE  8
     C                     PARM           P$RTN   1
     C           P$RTN     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     1599
     C                     MOVELER,16     D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      * TRUCK#(13)
     C           D1SURT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     12  99
     C                     MOVELER,2      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KEY1      SETGTAL#PLC1
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY1      REDPEAL#PLC1                  91
     C   91                LEAVE
     C           C5SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           C5SKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     121599
     C                     MOVELER,3      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
      * CUST.(13)
     C           D1TOKU    IFEQ 0                                      E
     C                     SETON                     13  99
     C                     MOVELER,4      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1TOKU    CHAINFGBPL01              91                E
     C  N90      B2SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     SETON                     91
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     13  99
     C                     MOVELER,5      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
      * DELIV.(14)
     C           D1NONY    IFEQ 0                                      E
     C                     SETON                     14  99
     C                     MOVELER,6      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           D1NONY    CHAINFGBPL01              91                E
     C  N90      B2SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     SETON                     91
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     SETON                     14  99
     C                     MOVELER,7      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     MOVELB2SMEI    D2NAME
      * FACT  (15)
     C***        D1NKOJ    IFEQ *BLANK                                 E
     C***                  SETON                     15  99
     C***                  MOVELER,8      D1ERR
     C***                  GOTO $CHK1Z
     C***                  ENDIF
     C*
     C**                   MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN
     C**
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     KFLD           D1DATE           STARTING DATE
     C                     KFLD           D1TOKU           COSTOMER CODE
     C                     KFLD           D1NONY           DELIVERY CODE
      *
     C           KEY01     SETLLAL#PPG1
      *-------------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY01     READEAL#PPG1                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C           CGSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           CGSKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C* DATA EXIST
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *-------------------------
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C                     MOVEA'1111'    *IN,11
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELER,9      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '1'                        :CHANGE
     C                     MOVEA'1111'    *IN,11
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELER,10     D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '2'                        :ADD
     C                     MOVEA'11011'   *IN,11
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELER,11     D1ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK1Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C**
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2UK
     C** SET MASTER VALUE
     C                     EXSR ##UKE
     C**                   MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN
     C                     MOVEA@UK       D2UK
      *
      *-------------------------
     C           $CHK1Z    TAG
      *-------------------------
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
     C           ##UKE     BEGSR
     C           KEY02     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     KFLD           D1DATE           CHANGE DATE
     C                     KFLD           D1TOKU           COSTOMER CODE
     C                     KFLD           D1NONY           DELIVERY CODE
     C                     KFLD           D1NKOJ           DELIVERY FACTORY
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         Z       40
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @UK
     C           KEY02     SETLLAL#PPG1
      *-------------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY02     READEAL#PPG1                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C           CGSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           CGSKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ADD  1         Z
     C           Z         IFLE 40
     C                     MOVELCGNUKE    @UK,Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *-------------------------
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      * DSP 2
      *================================================================
     C           #DSP2     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     EXFMTDSP02
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,21           21 - 28
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,29           29 - 36
     C                     MOVEA'00000000'*IN,37           37 - 44
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D2ERR
      *--------------------
     C                     SELEC
     C** < F3 >
     C           *INKC     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
     C** < F5 >
     C           *INKE     WHEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2 F5'@STEP
     C**
     C                     OTHER
     C                     MOVE '#CHK2   '@STEP
     C                     ENDSL
      *--------------------
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *          DSP2 CHECK
      *================================================================
     C           #CHK2     BEGSR
     C**
     C           1         DO   40        X       40
     C           D2UK,X    IFNE *BLANK
     C           X         ANDLT40
     C                     Z-ADDX         Z
     C*
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     ADD  1         Z
     C           D2UK,X    IFEQ D2UK,Z
     C                     ADD  20        Z
     C                     MOVE '1'       *IN,Z
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVELER,12     D2ERR
     C                     GOTO $CHK2Z
     C                     ENDIF
     C           Z         IFEQ 40
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C**
      *-------------------------
     C           $CHK2Z    TAG
      *-------------------------
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C           @STEP     ANDEQ'#CHK2 F5'
     C                     MOVE '#UPD    '@STEP
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE '#DSP2   '@STEP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *
      *================================================================
     C           #UPD      BEGSR
      *-------------------------
      *   :CANCEL
      *-------------------------
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '0'                        :CANCEL
     C           KEY01     SETLLAL#PPG1
     C*--------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY01     READEAL#PPG1                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C           CGSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           CGSKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVE 'D'       CGSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    CGSKHZ
     C                     UPDATAL#PPG11
     C                     ENDDO
     C*--------------------
     C                     ENDIF
      *-------------------------
      *   :ADD
      *-------------------------
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '2'                        :ADD
     C*
     C           D2UKX     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVEAD2UK      @UK
     C                     Z-ADDD1DATE    $$KIHZ  80       CHANGE DATE
     C                     EXSR ##WRT
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
      *-------------------------
      *   :CHANGE
      *-------------------------
     C           D1KKBN    IFEQ '1'                        :CHANGE
     C*
     C                     Z-ADDD1DATE    K$KIHZ  80       CHANGE DATE
     C                     EXSR ##DLT
     C*
     C           D2UKX     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVEAD2UK      @UK
     C                     Z-ADDD1DATE    $$KIHZ  80       CHANGE DATE
     C                     EXSR ##WRT
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
      *-------------------------
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1KKBN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1SURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADD3411      D1TOKU           COSTOMER CODE
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1NONY           DELIVERY CODE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1NKOJ           DELIVERY FACTORY
     C                     MOVE '#DSP1   '@STEP
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
      *         変更前データを削除
      *================================================================
     C           ##DLT     BEGSR
     C           KEY02     SETLLAL#PPG1
     C*--------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY02     READEAL#PPG1                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C           CGSKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           CGSKHZ    ANDLE@SYSHZ
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     MOVE 'D'       CGSKJY
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    CGSKHZ
     C                     UPDATAL#PPG11
     C                     ENDDO
     C*--------------------
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
     C           ##WRT     BEGSR
      *================================================================
      *
     C           1         DO   40        X
     C           @UK,X     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL@UK,X     K1NUKE           DOCK
      *
     C           KEY03     CHAINAL#PPG1              91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    CGSKJY           DELETE CODE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     CGSKHZ           DELETE CODE
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    CGKOHZ           UPDATE WORK DATE
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSTM    CGKOTI           UPDATE WORK TIME
     C                     MOVELW#USER    CGKOME           UPDATE TEAM MEMBER
     C                     UPDATAL#PPG11
      *
     C                     ELSE
      * WRITE
     C                     CLEARAL#PPG11
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSHZ    CGKOHZ           UPDATE WORK DATE
     C                     Z-ADD@SYSTM    CGKOTI           UPDATE WORK TIME
     C                     MOVELW#USER    CGKOME           UPDATE TEAM MEMBER
     C                     Z-ADDD1TOKU    CGTOKU           CUSTOMER CODE
     C                     Z-ADDD1NONY    CGNONY           DELIVERY CODE
     C                     MOVELD1NKOJ    CGNKOJ           DELIVERY FACTORY
     C                     MOVELK1NUKE    CGNUKE           DOCK
     C                     MOVELD1SURT    CGSURT           SUB ROUTE
     C                     Z-ADD$$KIHZ    CGKIHZ           CHANGE DATE
     C                     WRITEAL#PPG11
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
      *================================================================
**
ER-1 INPUT UPDATE (1 2 3)
ER-2 INPUT TRUCK#
ER-3 TRUCK# IS NOT IN M/F
ER-4 INPUT CUST.
ER-5 CUST. CODE IS NOT IN DETAILS M/F
ER-6 INPUT DELIV.
ER-7 DRLIV. CODE IS NOT IN DETAILS M/F
ER-8 INPUT FACT
ER-9 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F DON'T EXIST
ER-10 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F DON'T EXIST
ER-11 ADD WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F EXIST
ER-12 OVERLAP
ER-13 INPUT CHANGE DATE
ER-14 CHANGE DATE ERROR
ER-15 INPUT DATE
ER-16 INPUT DATE ERROR
